...Create time-saving right click shortcuts (Windows Vista or Later)

...Sometimes desktop of your PC is cluttered with lots of shortcuts. These issue is easily solved by Right Click Shortcuts Creator tool of Right Click Enhancer Professional. Right Click Shortcuts Creator allows you to add applications, files and folder shortcuts to your right click context menu.
...Doesn't want to add more stuffs directly into right click then you can also create sub menus if you have Windows 7 or Windows 8. You can add applications, files and folder shortcuts to these sub menus for ease of access and better organization.

...You can add command line arguments to the application shortcuts as well as edit previously added shortcuts and sub menus with ease. There is built in HTML help files to guide you through the process of creating, editing or deleting right click shortcuts and sub menus.
...Your PC and right click menu performance will be uneffected no matter how many shortcuts or sub menus you add in your right click context menu.
 &lt;a href=&quot;
